            "title": "《大手成交》盈富基金10分鐘內4手自動交叉盤,共涉1.1億元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社3日專訊》盈富基金(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02800:STOCK:ETF\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02800\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02800-HK</a>)於9:52am錄得1手140.25萬股自動交叉盤,每股造23.2元,較上日收市價低1.4%,涉資3254萬元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　盈富基金早於9:49am錄得1手93.95萬股自動交叉盤,每股造23.24元,較上日收市價低1.2%,涉資2183萬元。另於9:47am錄得1手133.9萬股自動交叉盤,每股造23.22元,較上日收市價低1.3%,涉資3109萬元。另於9:42am錄得1手107.05萬股自動交叉盤,每股造23.1元,較上日收市價低1.8%,涉資2473萬元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　4手自動交叉盤共涉475.15萬股,涉資共1.1億元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　盈富基金現價跌1.4%,報23.18元;成交8695萬股,成交金額20.12億元,主動買沽比率49:51,資金淨主動賣出4088萬元。(rw)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
