            "id": 5921496,
            "title": "《異動股》申洲國際跌幅擴大至17%,關稅戰殺至出口敏感股重挫",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社3日專訊》美國總統特朗普「關稅日」殺到,針對世界各地貿易夥伴的對等關稅計劃,特朗普宣布的一系列對等關稅中,將對中國進口貨品加徵34%額外關稅,令關稅累積高達54%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　出口敏感股急挫,申洲國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02313-HK</a>)跌幅擴大至17.1%,報51.3元;比亞迪電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00285-HK</a>)跌4.8%,報38.7元;創科實業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00669-HK</a>)跌8.4%,報85.9元;美的集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00300:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00300\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00300-HK</a>)跌3.7%,報73.8元;瑞聲科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02018:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02018\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02018-HK</a>)跌8%,報43.6元;敏實集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00425:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00425\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00425-HK</a>)跌5.3%,報20.35元。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報22950,跌252點或跌1.1%,主板成交近527億元。國企指數報8436,跌95點或跌1.1%。恒生科技指數報5367,跌59點或跌1.1%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　即月期指新報22927,跌282點,低水23點。即月國指期貨報8419,跌104點,低水17點。即月科指期貨新報5362,跌67點,低水5點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>申洲國際(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02313:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02313\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02313-HK</a>)</td><td>51.3元</td><td>跌17.06%</td></tr><tr><td>比亞迪電子(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00285:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00285\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00285-HK</a>)</td><td>38.7元</td><td>跌4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>創科實業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00669:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00669\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00669-HK</a>)</td><td>85.9元</td><td>跌8.42%</td></tr><tr><td>美的集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00300:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00300\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=